782
00:45:26,333 --> 00:45:27,166
[squawks]

783
00:45:34,625 --> 00:45:36,625
[melancholy music continues]

784
00:45:40,458 --> 00:45:41,750
[cheeping]

785
00:45:48,958 --> 00:45:50,958
