- [Sam] Oh.

802
00:47:07,791 --> 00:47:09,000
Next time.

803
00:47:11,083 --> 00:47:12,083
[shutter clicking]

804
00:47:13,291 --> 00:47:14,250
[shutter clicking]

805
00:47:20,291 --> 00:47:22,291
Maybe we should try something different.

806
00:47:23,625 --> 00:47:24,458
Oh.

807
00:47:25,083 --> 00:47:26,083
