822
00:48:08,583 --> 00:48:11,833
- I wanna walk the boys to school.
- Let's go for a skate.

823
00:48:11,916 --> 00:48:13,958
[Sam] I wanna get dressed by myself.

824
00:48:14,541 --> 00:48:16,291
